criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          1. T2DM patients diagnosed ≤ 6 months according to the WHO criteria (WHO, 1999);

          2. age ≥18 years;

          3. permanent residents of Xi'an;

          4. no mental disorders;

          5. voluntary to participate in the study.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          1. patients with terminal illness;

          2. physically disabled patients;

          3. taking part in other studies;

          4. with aural or visual problems.
